Buffett’s Annual Charity Lunch Auction to Seek Bids From June 5

-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 
2011-05-10T18:02:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/buffett-sets-annual-lunch-auction-on-ebay-to-benefit-san-francisco-charity.html
Warren Buffett ’s annual charity lunch
auction, which raised $2.6 million last year, will accept bids
on  EBay Inc. (EBAY)  from June 5 to June 10.  The bidding for a lunch date with the billionaire investor
starts at $25,000, according to an e-mailed statement sent today
by San Francisco-based charity  Glide , which has reaped nearly
$9 million from the annual event in more than 10 years.  Glide Lunch With Warren Buffett Results:  Year  Winner                                        Winning Bid
2000  Anonymous                                         $25,000
2001  Anonymous                                         $18,000
2002  Anonymous                                         $25,000
